import React from 'react'
import ReactDOM from 'react-dom'
import App from "./App" 
import "./index.css"
import Sdata from "./Sdata"



ReactDOM.render(
        <>
        <hi> Most Watched Netflix Webseries </hi>
         <App 
         imgsrc={Sdata[0].imgsrc}
         title={Sdata[0].title}
         sname= {Sdata[0].sname}
         link={Sdata[0].link} />
        
        <App 
         imgsrc="riverdale.jpg"
         title="nnnnnnnnnn"
         sname= "RiverDale"
         link="https://www.netflix.com/in/title/80133311"/> 

        <App 
         imgsrc="peaky_blinders.jpg"
         title="nnnnnnnnnn"
         sname= "Peaky Blinders"
         link="https://www.netflix.com/in/title/80002479"/> 


<App 
         imgsrc="DarkNetflixPosterEnglish.jpg"
         title="nnnnnnnnnn"
         sname= "Money Heist"
         link="https://www.netflix.com/in/title/80192098"/> 
        
        <App 
         imgsrc="StrangerThings.webp"
         title="nnnnnnnnnn"
         sname= "Stranger Things"
         link="https://www.netflix.com/in/title/80057281"/> 
         
         
        </>



, document.getElementById('root'))
